  "description": "Sleek visuals for a better gameplay: clearer spyglass, clearer stained glass, rainbow XP, ...",
  "body": "<h1>TK's Textures</h1>\n<h4>Sleek visuals for a better gameplay</h4>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\nFollowing changes are currently included in the pack:\n- spyglass-view now only shows the border, making it more transparent\n- all stained glass blocks are now more transparent (removed the semi translucent parts)\n- the experience bar is now rainbow colored\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/sd51Tkr9/glass-compare.png\" alt=\"glass-compare\" width=\"250\" />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Pvp4hnzZ/spyglass-compare.png\" alt=\"spyglass-compare\" width=\"500\" />\n\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nRZZ43X/divider-dark-green.png\" alt=\"divider\" width=\"1903\" height=\"10\" /></p>\n\nif you have any questions about the mod, or you want a few insights about upcoming features:\n<br>\nfeel free to join the Discord &nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">\n    <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VQ66pHN/Discord.png\" alt=\"Divider\" width=\"166\" height=\"32\" />\n</a>\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n<a title=\"discord\" href=\"https://discord.gg/bhUaWhq\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">link</a>\n",
